      <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0;">Options may include words that sound similar (e.g., 一時 vs 七時, 火曜日 vs 木曜日). Listen carefully for exact numbers and days.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fca5a5; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 8px;">
      <strong style="color: #dc2626;">🪤 Trap 3: Partial Truth</strong>
